author: ruchithf
msg: Updated security module to be activated by a service/client that requires WS-Security functionality. When the security module is engaged (globally) if a certain service/client requires it to be activated on the inflow or the outflow <parameter name='InflowSecurity'>on</parameter> or <parameter name='OutflowSecurity'>on</parameter> set accordingly in the services.xml or axis2.xml respectively. To turn any of the options off set the paramter value to 'off'
